1.m_mText: "In the cycle of rebirth, turn to dust along with time itself."
"The end of one world is merely the dawn of another."
"So my consciousness... fades away..."
"How dreadfully dull."
"Perhaps there is still a chance to break free from this cycle."
"I hope to find at least a modicum of enjoyment in this..."
"An inevitable outcome."
"I am but a wanderer, blind to the future, endlessly roaming at the edge of time."
"Do you wish to glimpse the secrets of time through me?"
"I've experienced this sensation before..."
"The consciousness deep within my soul gradually awakens."
"Even the hardest stone will be ground to sand by time... as will I."
"The hands of the pocket watch have turned."
"I'll accept it for now. This, too, is part of the rules."
"So my heart still beats after all..."
"It seems you have freed me from the shackles of time."
"I hope my presence doesn't make you uncomfortable."
"The time frozen around me seems to flow once more..."
"Could you maintain some distance?"
"Time has no end, only the solitude of eternity."
"My ties to this world were severed by time long ago."
"One day, I shall open my eyes at the boundless edge of time."
"Listen to the seedlings breaking through the soil."
"Feel the pulse of life."
"I shall... wither..."
"I'll do my best."
"Life sprouts here."
"I've become more vibrant."
"There's still a gap between knowledge and real battle."
"If needed, I can share my knowledge with you."
"Would you accompany me to the herb garden?"
"Knowledge is boundless."
"An enlightening experience."
"In my leisure, I also enjoy quietly contemplating things."
"How does this work exactly?"
"As a token of gratitude, I will mend your wounds next time."
"Having you by my side puts me at ease."
"I never thought I'd care for someone else like this..."
"Are you feeling unwell?"
"If you don't mind, please close your eyes and listen to the whispers of the flowers and plants."
"That's not very polite, you know."
"So this is how the plants feel when I touch them..."
"Ignorance is a sin in itself."
"Your thirst for knowledge is stronger than I anticipated."
"Be lost in the dream."
"Do you still remember this dream?"
"I'm sinking... into the shadow..."
"Gone with the dream."
"Embrace the dream."
"Wake from the illusion."
"That was no dream."
"I have heard your call, master."
"What beautiful dream would you like to have today?"
"New dreams, new inspirations."
"Classical, romantic, realistic, fantasy... I've collected so many dreamscapes."
"Dozing off already? I haven't even sung my lullaby..."
"Out of everyone, you chose me?"
"Is this my reward for completing my task?"
"Is it time to take the next step?"
"I am with you, until eternity."
"Ah, no, it's just... this is a little sudden."
"If that is your wish, I can oblige."
"Would you like me to help you fall asleep?"
"For my next reward... I'd like to fall asleep together and dream."
"Are you practicing? It's more effective to set the reward and punishment first."
"This is what you desire? Then... I shall weave the perfect dream for you."
"Let us honor the sacrifices that led us here."
"Black Blood can be cured. But there are many things that can't be."
"Do you need me to examine you?"
"...That's not necessary."
"To gain something... something else must be given."
"Are you feeling unwell? You've just been standing there."
"Life has grown even more burdensome."
"This is for me? Thank you."
"Come closer. Let me feel the warmth of your presence."
"Promise me you'll stay safe, okay? I couldn't bear to see your wounds."
"The world is constantly being renewed, and destroyed."
"...Forgive me. Now is not the time to let go of all restraint."
"I don't mind revealing my true face, but it's better for both of us if I don't."
"The sensation of your touch... I shall engrave it deeply in my heart."
"Humans cannot resist the will of the gods."
"Perhaps we were fated to never truly understand one another."
"Witness the advent of flame!"
"Ignite the darkness."
"Blaze for me once more..."
"I guess I'll get a bit serious."
"You call me the 'Beguiler,' yet offer something so irresistible?"
"Well, there goes my excuse for slacking off..."
"You've certainly caused me quite a bit of trouble."
"As long as the flame still burns, even death can be warm... Care to try?"
"Accursed by flame, condemned to burn until the end of days."
"Phew, this fiery passion is getting intense!"
"We witness the blaze of life burning bright, until time turns it all to ashes."
"Your gaze feels even hotter than my flames. Is it getting warm in here, or is it just me?"
"This time, perhaps we can change the future..."
"What a hassle... Picking out a gift in return is no easy task, you know?"
"Once, someone tried to fly toward the sun. Can you guess what befell them?"
"I never imagined it would be you by my side... No, I'm glad it is you."
"Careful, it's quite scorching."
"What is birthed from the flames is not civilization, but countless wars."
"Ah... I have already drifted off to sleep. All I utter now is but sleep talk."
"The gods are merely tools to reach the future. And as tools, there must be someone to wield them."
"Admiration is the furthest cry from understanding. You have my regrets."
"What I yearn for are not followers dependent on me, but kindling that can burn alongside me."
"This shall be the final requiem."
"Divine retribution approaches."
"Do not mourn for me..."
"The Lance of God awaits here."
"With this power, I shall slay our enemies more efficiently."
"My body seems to be growing restless..."
"Awaiting the next Task."
"The Church gave me a title, but the children’s voices gave me my name."
"Do you have a new task?"
"I have been blessed."
"The feeling deep within my mind... so strange."
"Who... am I, really?"
"This scene feels oddly familiar..."
"I will treasure this."
"May I... come a little closer?"
"This strange impulse in my heart... What could it be?"
"Are you expressing your friendliness?"
"Your scent... it seems to awaken memories within me. Please, would you come closer?"
"This sensation feels strange to me."
"I can't remember who I am, but... I don't think I belong to the Church."
"What do you expect from this cold, lifeless body?"
"I never thought my heart, long grown cold, could burn so fiercely again..."
"I'll send you to your grave."
"There's no escape."
"This humiliation... how fitting..."
"I see the target."
"I want more."
"Have I earned the right to live?"
"Mission accomplished. Target has been eliminated."
"I'm Selena Dalma, hired assassin on occasion... Oh, you're glaring at me..."
"Oh... Wh-What a coincidence... running into you here..."
"You're using your precious resources on me? Hmm..."
"Even someone like me... I will follow... No, pursue you for life!"
"I'm being ignored... Okay, I don't mind. Not at all."
"Is... is this really happening?"
"Is this a bounty? Strange, I haven't taken any jobs recently."
"Really? You better not be lying... Liars have to swallow a thousand arrows."
"No one has ever been this kind to me... Thank you for giving me a place to return to."
"And just what do you think you're doing?"
"So, um, when vampires bite people... isn't it kind of intimate? Don't you... get embarrassed?"
"Hmph, you'd best watch your back at night!"
"Don't tug on my scarf... Ah, it's coming loose! Waahhh..."
"You'll pay for this."
"Hey, we all have to make due with what we were given, okay?"
"Cycles entwined, all consumed and laid to rest."
"Life, death, tell me what you seek."
"Darkness... is where I truly belong..."
"We shall release them from their torment."
"Birth is not the beginning, death not the end."
"Unforgotten, the cycle endures eternally."
"No death is without regret, only cold oblivion."
"So I never lost my memories, I just chose not to remember."
"Only by breaking free from the gravity of our past can we soar towards the starry sea of our future."
"Growth is the process of discovering oneself."
"I should no longer run from my true self."
"What's come over me, lost in thought while gazing at my reflection."
"Am I the one who remains stagnant?"
"Sometimes, one should reward oneself."
"The joy of a long life lies in rediscovering oneself time and again."
"To truly love one's fate and embrace oneself, that is the greatest courage of all."
"It takes considerable resolve to touch the embodiment of death."
"One such as I should no longer get close to anyone...except myself."
"Is the silver-white a symbol of decay, or of emptiness?"
"You have always been able to see the world through my eyes. Now, at last, I can see yours as well."
"Do you also experience this feeling of being watched from places hard to comprehend?"
"You are me in another place. This resonance of memories is the best proof."
"Purify the tainted souls."
"Repent at your leisure!"
"Justice... shall never perish..."
"The hour of execution has come."
"All is for the sake of justice."
"This power shall root out the wicked."
"Before the face of justice, what chance do evil and intrigue stand?"
"Nothing can shake my conviction."
"Setting the chaotic world right... That is my life's purpose!"
"Another step forward."
"I'm getting closer to... the ultimate answer."
"Have you also begun to feel lost in the darkness of this world?"
"It's time to get ready..."
"Oh, this is... for me?"
"Are you also searching for justice?"
"Perhaps I should rethink the meaning of justice... through your perspective."
"Oh you wanna train together? I'm afraid I don't have the time at the moment."
"Your hand... Could you keep holding mine a little longer? I fear I may lose my way..."
"These injuries are nothing. I'm strong!"
"I sense a different kind of justice in you... I see... True justice is tested after one gains power."
"An alchemist's tools aren't for prying eyes!"
"You've earned my approval. I shall let you witness the source of this explosive power!"
"Repent before the thunder!"
"I shall crush you with my might!"
"Fall back for now."
"It's my turn."
"Relish the thrill of battle."
"This feeling... Are there any worthy opponents to fight?"
"The battle's over already?"
"I hope you can put up a fight, or it won't be any fun."
"This time, I hope you can fight by my side until the very end."
"I feel the power you've bestowed upon me."
"The sword stands upon a mound of bones, fulfilling an oath to the dead."
"Are you trying to find my weakness?"
"Will you join me in this sacred rite?"
"Why are you giving this to me?"
"My heart yearns for baptism by battle."
"With you, perhaps I can really feel alive."
"From the moment one steps onto the battlefield, the Lord shows no favoritism to anyone."
"Peace nurtures the seeds of war, yet war, in turn, nurtures peace."
"When humanity is tainted by evil, the Lord shall bring punishment through the fires of war."
"I strive to hold back the tides of war, to keep you safe behind me."
"Only those who have strayed know the value of the right path."
"It seems the battlefield you seek is elsewhere... No matter, allow me to accompany you."
"I grant you a proper death."
"Ignorance, too, is a form of evil."
"So this is... Death..."
"We fight to bring peace."
"I still have strength to spare."
"I'm in my element."
"We're victorious... for the moment."
"Just Ottavia will do. The rest is irrelevant."
"My wish is simple: let the wicked die as they deserve, and the good meet their end with grace. Nothing more."
"There is still room to improve."
"Have I surpassed the old man now...? No, never mind."
"You're quite content to sit there, aren't you? Well, don't blame me if I take the lead."
"Oh? I didn't know this was possible."
"It's not exactly novel, but I can tell you put some thought into it. Thanks."
"You're proving to be somewhat trustworthy."
"Hey, don't go dying on me. You make a pretty good adventuring partner."
"Let's hope your death isn't too unsightly."
"I won't let you die for now, but this doesn't mean you're absolved."
"Chivalrous? You flatter me. I simply cannot stand injustice."
"After meeting you, I am even more convinced that a meaningless life is not destined, but an excuse for the weak-willed."
"You've heard tales of my swordsmanship? Haha, perhaps you heard wrong."
"I forget you're quite skilled with a sword too. Why don't you go inherit my title? You're far more suited than I."
"This is proof of my return from hell!"
"You're finished!"
"I'm still... not ready..."
"It's finally my turn!"
"The past me is gone."
"With this power, I can protect everyone!"
"It's not enough... I've yet to reach my limit!"
"The inverse butterfly flutters its wings, bringing both clear skies and tumultuous storms..."
"Don't come too close. I don't want you to get hurt."
"Have I still not adapted to this power...?"
"From now on, I'll be the one protecting you!"
"If I could choose again, perhaps I would have stayed here as the girl I once was."
"These enhancements are woefully inadequate..."
"I will treasure this."
"I've always been right here by your side."
"Let time stand still for a moment. I want to savor this lingering warmth."
"Only bitterness and regret remain, buried deep in my memories."
"It's the pain of the past that reminds me I'm still alive."
"Don't move. I'm... afraid I might lose control."
"Though I've been born anew, my heart remains unchanged."
"Now's not the time for such things."
"If I can be of assistance to you... perhaps this power isn't as terrible as I once believed."
"Steel yourself to bear the weight of life."
"Life flows."
"From deadwood, new buds shall sprout..."
"What restless creatures they are."
"It seems this vessel is not destined to wither yet."
"Can you smell it? This is the fragrance of life's fruit."
"Bury them well and let nature embrace their souls."
"All things in this world will eventually turn to dust, absorb the rain and dew, and sprout anew. That is life."
"Come closer, and let me whisper nature's secrets to you."
"The tender shoots are about to break through the earth..."
"Now I can linger in this world a while longer."
"One must savor these rare moments of tranquility."
"Nature is calling out to my soul..."
"Thank you for the things you have painstakingly prepared for me."
"Plants are not without hearts..."
"Our lives seem to be intertwined like branches."
"This form marks the humanity I've forsaken."
"Life has a beginning and an end, yet plants can endure eternally..."
"Humans... such despicable creatures. Become my sustenance."
"Plants can shatter the shackles of time and grasp the breadth of the soul."
"Linger a moment longer, and you will feel the resonance of the plants."
"What you touch is not flesh, but the life flowing beneath the skin."
"Plunge into the turbid currents of fate."
"Cease your struggle."
"I'm... so cold..."
"Desire beckons."
"The chill fades away..."
"Descending into greater depths..."
"It's time to return."
"Would you like to see my homeland, buried deep beneath the waves?"
"Are you sure it's alright to be wandering around when there's still so much work to be done?"
"You really won't let me rest, will you?"
"Sigh... let me handle the troublesome stuff from now on."
"You keep staring at me. Is there something you need?"
"Very well, I'll humor you for a bit."
"Since you prepared this for me, I'll accept it."
"I felt your warmth once again."
"If one cannot break free from the shackles of desire, then one must learn to live with its presence... Right?"
"Being handsy is not a desirable quality."
"Eek...! Does teasing me really bring you such joy? What a terrifying fetish."
"Rest assured, no dust will settle on my head."
"You want to share the burden of my thoughts? With you here, I've learned to let go of them."
"There's nothing here but darkness. You should know that."
"There was once only emptiness here, but it is precisely because of that, that it can hold this warmth."
"A blunt axe be all I need to claim thy head!"
"'Tis the soul-piercin' chill from the very depths!"
"This aunciente one...yields not...!"
"Allow this auncient one to enlighten thee on the nature of power."
"Such pure, unbridled might of the spirit..."
"The Soul is the most perfect form of life."
"While this auncient one draws breath, ne'er shall victory be ceded!"
"The strong devour the weak. Only the victors will be remembered."
"Ah, tranquility... it's been too long."
"This meagre enhancement isn't even enough to pick my teeth with."
"This ancient soul still burns!"
"Speak your mind, if you've aught to say."
"Not enough... I need more!"
"You have my thanks."
"Is this the resonance of souls?"
"Hmph, you are the second to earn my respect. Or perhaps, you were also the first."
"Shall I help you shed the shackles of the flesh as well...?"
"The secret to immortality... does it pique your interest?"
"What truly defines a person - their physical form, or their soul?"
"Your gaze reminds this old warrior of the days when I still possessed mortal flesh."
"This armor can offer you naught but cold."
"Were it not for the shackles of this armor, perhaps I could understand the likes of you."
"I apologize, but you will fall beneath my blade."
"Please grant me courage."
"This can't be the end..."
"Crush the enemy."
"I... shall not waver."
"This sword will cut through everything."
"I have protected once more."
"Clive Ganelon, Gravekeeper of the Forbidden Grounds."
"I wield my blade to protect friends and kin."
"My sword has grown a bit stronger."
"This power was born solely for protection, nothing more."
"Until the day this greatsword rusts, I will let none come to harm."
"My body... it creaks and groans..."
"This kindness, I shall cherish for a lifetime!"
"So this is what lies within your heart..."
"Henceforth, I shall fight and perish for your sake."
"If humans were to don the pelts of beasts, could they still retain a human heart..."
"You... have known all along, haven't you? That this is an unbreakable cycle."
"I shall guard the forbidden grounds, for all eternity..."
"Every time I open my eyes, it marks the beginning of a tragedy. But this time... I have you by my side."
"Breathing tears through my flesh like a blade, but it also reminds me of my own cowardice."
"I entrust my future to you."
"I too... can protect everyone!"
"I can't stop now..."
"I'm sorry..."
"Are you... sure?"
"My body... It feels different somehow."
"Does this mean I'm a grown-up now?"
"Is this a dream? Did I... really win?"
"If there's anything I can do... No, please let me help you!"
"What do I need to do to get stronger... Ah! It's, it's nothing, just talking to myself..."
"Will this make me stronger...?"
"I've finally caught up to you."
"You've been quiet... Did I do something wrong?"
"I have to keep pushing myself!"
"I-is this really for me?"
"Please don't be so kind to me..."
"I won't let you down... I absolutely won't!"
"I fear the darkness, yet I cannot touch the light."
"Could you... let me feel your warmth again?"
"If only I had more time, perhaps I could truly grow and mature."
"I tiptoe to be closer to you, but you're still out of reach."
"Do you think I'm just some kid too?!"
"To protect everyone... I must become stronger."
"The grand finale, by yours truly!"
"I will guide them in the only right direction."
"Even in sinking, such beauty..."
"The El Dorado sets sail in all her splendor!"
"Captivated by my valiant prowess on the battlefield, are you?"
"How beautiful... the El Dorado never disappoints."
"The El Dorado returns, her hold overflowing with the spoils of victory!"
"Impress me, and I may consider allowing you aboard the El Dorado."
"Don't dare avert your gaze. Miss my splendor, and you'll regret it dearly."
"More power..."
"Tell me, was that gold you saw, or just my brilliance?"
"What's this? Has my irresistible charm struck you speechless?"
"This place could use a serious refit."
"You should know that such meager attempts at appeasement will hardly suffice."
"Speak, then. What reward do you seek from me?"
"The show is about to begin… shall we walk into it together?"
"Oh? Do you covet a bespoke ensemble such as mine?"
"Like the silk? I'll send a set your way."
"You desire a self-portrait of mine? Fret not, for I can indulge this trifling request of yours."
"My future is but a dream of endlessly prayer to return to the bygone days."
"Gold... 'Tis a thing of beauty, is it not? Dazzling, never fading—precisely what I seek."
"Gold lasts forever... and maybe what we've built does too."
"Consider it an honor to be granted death by my hand!"
"Resistance is futile."
"Is this... pain?"
"Become my nourishment."
"This pleasure is truly unforgettable."
"Let us begin constructing a paradise of flesh and blood."
"Cattle, grovel on the ground like the livestock you are."
"As the first to dare approach me, perhaps I should grant you a reward... How about some human blood?"
"May I have a taste of you?"
"The blood wails in agony..."
"This sense of fulfillment, of being filled to the brim... I crave more."
"Ah, the melodious sound of blood coursing through the body. It's music to my ears."
"The limit hasn't been reached. Not yet."
"I desire you more than this trivial offering."
"Do you wish to offer your blood to me?"
"You shan't escape my grasp. Not until I have the world in my hands."
"If even the gods had flesh and blood... I wonder, what exquisite flavor would they yield?"
"Humans, gods, the Church... nothing more than pieces of flesh destined to rot away."
"Blood is my only craving."
"Stand by my side and witness how I toy with this world."
"Don't forget, your ability to stay by my side is the reward I've bestowed upon you."
"Don't even think about leaving my side. If you do, you'll be like blood separated from its vessel - nothing but a filthy puddle."
"The past, without end, becomes this moment. And the future, without limit, begins from here."
"Lunar Abyss."
"Failed... my duty..."
"Past or future, every 'me' stands with you now."
"Countless victories guide us to the next battle. Yet a single defeat may summon eternal silence."
"You've arrived, ender of cycles. This is where time itself comes to rest."
"I remember you, Vassal of the Bathory, a drifter from Sunset Isle, a sacrifice bound to the seal… and Noah Nevernight, who has walked with me through uncountable pasts."
"A fragment of another Aiona's power… now gathered here."
"As I am now… can I truly withstand the erosion of time?"
"The fire that devours time could awaken at any moment. I mustn't rest here."
"Use my strength—if it means a future for all."
"Is this a token from your 'now'? Then I'll keep it close."
"When even my own existence begins to blur… thinking of you gives me the strength to go on."
"The duty I uphold, is for the flow of time, for the world's future… and for you."
"In the desert of time, the body no longer matters."
"A touch like this… reminds me I'm still alive."
"So many memories crowd my mind. At times, I lose myself within them."
"In the fractured shards of time, I see you—walking with me toward the future."
"This is the duty of the Alitas… and my fate to bear."
"Perhaps soon… we'll break these chains together."
"For the continuity of time."
"Where my heart leads, there lies my home."
"I'll protect everything I hold dear."
"Don't... concern yourself with me."
"Please, be gentle with those flowers."
"For the sake of peace."
"I've read about the day, but for as long as I can remember, night has always been our natural state."
"Borders are drawn by people. Flowers don't understand such things—that's why they bloom so brilliantly."
"I must strive harder."
"Does this version of me finally count as 'useful'?"
"Fate is a like shackle. Those ensnared spend their lives as puppets, like dolls dancing at a recital."
"Is this... a new ritual of the Hall of the Elders?"
"Is this... what it feels like to be cared for?"
"You seem... different from the other Bloodborn."
"Thank you for illuminating this darkness. It seems a new dawn awaits, beyond the edge of prophecy."
"Are you also... a messenger from the future?"
"Before I met you, the Moonblessed were but a beautiful legend. Now, my yearning has true form."
"This is... Mother's color."
"Might I rest in the warmth of your palm, just for a moment?"
"Shall we share an umbrella?"
"Come. With this umbrella, we can venture into places kissed by sunlight."
"I shall traverse every realm beneath my stride!"
"History stands still!"
"The map... it isn't finished yet..."
"Off we go! Which era shall we chart today?"
"That's what happens when you underestimate a cartographer!"
"I hear you're someone with stories... Allow me to separate the truth from the tales!"
"Tell me... might there be fascinating worlds hidden beyond the Cartographer's manual?"
"Well then... I suppose we can chart the flow of time itself?"
"Another step toward becoming the continent's greatest Cartographer."
"I've read every last journal left behind... it's always the same tired tales, over and over. How tedious."
"Everyone here seems to have such fascinating ‘stories.’"
"A Bloodborn custom, perhaps? How fascinating... I must document this for my records."
"Tell me... would you truly not consider joining our Cartographer's Guild?"
"Grandfather taught me that time flows in cycles... So I hope that at every turn of the wheel, I might encounter someone as remarkable as you."
"I sense we've crossed paths in some distant era... but in which epoch, I wonder?"
"I could take you back six centuries for a proper field study. In return, perhaps you'd give me a tour of that castle of yours?"
"Hey! That's not some Ganelon wolf tail, you know..."
"You're quite fond of head pats, aren't you? ...Could this be some sort of ceremonial ritual among the Bloodborn?"
"Careful—that's a cartographer's tool handed down from my grandfather."
"Curious about it? Let me show you the proper technique."
"Tonight, embrace your eternal slumber."
"Our promise… I can't keep it after all..."
"Need help, little one?"
"Finally, the troublemaker falls silent."
"Allow me to be your guide… through a most 'delightful' holiday in Sapphire Isle."
"Anywhere you want to go? I'll take you… anywhere."
"Like the flames of vengeance..."
"Come closer. Don't be afraid of how I look."
"(humming)… Ahem! Pretend you didn't see that."
"They trust me, so I'll protect them."
"Oh? Are you blushing?"
"I wonder... what kind of web should I weave to make you fall right into it?"
"Little one, would you like to become my 'family'?"
"That's not one of the perks covered by your custom coin."
"Looking to be spoiled, little one?"
"That's not how a gentleman behaves."
"Is this as far as you'll go? Or shall I show you how it's done?"
"Few have touched the blade of the Mistbound Terror… None of them still draw breath."
"Do you wish to be held... entangled... while sinking into the deep sea?"
"Let blood repay the weight of sin."
"A simple favor."
"There's no going back... to my home beneath the waves..."
"Who's on the death list tonight?"
"The slaughter is over."
"Wind guides, shadow strikes, and my arrows won't fall behind."
"Supplies matter too! (munching)"
"The debt I owe… I'll never be able to repay it."
"Make it quick! I've got seafood on the grill!"
"Well? I've got what it takes to be a Bell Ringer now, right?"
"I am Selena the Deadly Arrow, chief assistant to Silver-haired and first disciple of Lord Van Helsing!"
"Mr. customer, what'll it be—wait, it's you, Silver-haired."
"Now I can grill even more seafood at once!"
"Feels like my cooking's almost as sharp as my assassinations!"
"Huh? No jobs right now?"
"Ahem. From now on, I'm calling the shots."
"This thing... I don't have to pay for it, do I?"
"Silver-haired! I saved the best batch of seafood just for you."
"W-Why are you looking at me like that? I'm not… grilled seafood..."
"I'm already swamped. Don't make it worse."
"That's your idea of encouragement, Silver-haired? It's... quite unique."
"Welcome to the Fried Friar— Ugh, when will this job ever end..."
"Heh, admit it—I'm pretty good at this, huh?"
"When did the ingredients escape?"
"It's all sticky... Help me wipe it off!"
"Give me whatever job you've got. As long as it pays, I'm in."
"Bella: Take my thoughts with you… and keep walking forward."
"Bella: A promise… no matter what, must be fulfilled."
"Bella: This was the ending I should've faced… long ago."

"Bella: I still remember how to use 'power'.
Yakov: Remember to protect me, Little Bella!"

"Bella: We won… though this game wasn't much fun.
Yakov: So where's our prize, then?"

"Bella: I've been waiting for you. Let's go together this time.
Yakov: Don't forget me! I'm coming too!"

"Bella: Let's do something fun, shall we?
Yakov: Fun and profitable—now that's the dream!"
